OL,4,Cto be questioned by MPs
OL,6,FThe Horizon IT scandal saw more than
OL,7,F700 sub-postmasters handed criminal
OL,8,Fconvictions between 1999 and 2015 as
OL,9,FFujitsu's faulty Horizon system made
OL,10,Fit appear as though money was missing
OL,11,Fat their branches.
OL,13,FHundreds of sub-postmasters are still
OL,14,Fawaiting compensation despite the
OL,15,FGovernment announcing that those who
OL,16,Fhave had convictions quashed are
OL,17,Feligible for #600,000 payouts.
