OL,3,CEx-Post Office chairman Henry Staunton
OL,4,Cto be questioned by MPs
OL,6,FMr Staunton, who will answer questions
OL,7,Fon Tuesday afternoon, stepped down
OL,8,Ffrom the Post Office amid ongoing
OL,9,Ftensions last month.
OL,11,FThe former WHSmith executive has since
OL,12,Fbeen involved in a deepening row with
OL,13,FMs Badenoch after he claimed he had
OL,14,Fbeen told to delay payouts to the sub-
OL,15,Fpostmasters affected.
OL,17,FMs Badenoch tolds MPs he had spread
OL,18,F"made-up anecdotes" following his
OL,19,Fdismissal.
