OL,6,FHowever, ministers are under pressure
OL,7,Fover allegations a senior civil
OL,8,Fservant told Mr Staunton not to focus
OL,9,Fon "long-term issues" and to protect
OL,10,Fhis organisation's finances.
OL,12,FMr Staunton is said to have been told
OL,13,Fduring a meeting with Sarah Munby, who
OL,14,Fwas then permanent secretary at the
OL,15,FDepartment for Business, Energy and
OL,16,FIndustrial Strategy (BEIS), to
OL,17,F"hobble" into the next general
OL,18,Felection, according to notes reported
OL,19,Fby The Times newspaper.
