OL,6,FMs Badenoch then referred to the
OL,7,Fdispute last Thursday, tweeting: "It's
OL,8,Fimportant that people have trust in
OL,9,Fall we're doing to get them justice.
OL,11,F"It's frustrating dealing with false
OL,12,Fallegations that break that trust, but
OL,13,Fwe won't be distracted.
OL,15,F"The law is expected to come into
OL,16,Feffect by the end of July and apply to
OL,17,Fconvictions in England & Wales."
